  <title>KEY ASSIGNMENT SUMMARY FOR THE DRAGON 64</title>
  <para>On the Dragon 64 the
CLEAR key is used as the CONTROL key, where reference is made to
the CONTROL key, use the CLEAR key. For example, CONTROL-D is
achieved by holding down the CLEAR key and hitting the D key.</para>
